## Direction (locked)

- **Subject first:** Primary Group(s) required
- **Facets:** shape-driven atomic fields (reps / time / distance / load / set count) — show what was logged; never sum unlike units
- **Scope:** nest labels + variations / tools / set type = WHERE, not rival lenses
- **Multi-PG:** stacked panels (one per selected PG)
- **Saved Insights:** query templates with live re-run (**Phase 3**)
- **Category:** PG metadata for balance **saved views**, not home-screen lens
- **Read source:** `v_log_set_facts`; credit-each under the hood; complete logs only

## Shipped (Phase 2 MVP)

Draft query form on Insights tab: FOR → SHOW facets → WHERE (Scope disclosure) → IN dates. Load facet = avg when present (not tonnage). No persistence / lock yet.

## Phase 3 direction (Nate feel, Jul 22 — ideate before implement)

Builder parity: saved named queries (+ notes), dynamic vs static dates, per-PG scope cards (override analogy), lock ≈ Locked Preview grammar. Details in proposal §5–6 / §9 Phase 3 / §11 and `docs/Status.md` “Phase 2 feel → Phase 3 ideation”.

